### Common Issues & Fixes

**Issue**: Dialog not showing
- **Fix**: Check WindowInteropHelper.Owner assignment

**Issue**: No elements modified
- **Fix**: Check parameter write permissions and filtering

**Issue**: Slow on large projects
- **Fix**: Use Option 2 (exact match) instead of Option 1 (partial match)
